creator: WeHeal
descriptionHtml:
Completely Anonymous - Helps you get over problems of all kinds
Feel good Short Stories - Inspirational Quotes to make your day ❤️

Real people will help you sail through difficult times -

👤 Complete Anonymity.
💔 Heart Break
🤒 Illness
📔 Studies
👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Family Issues
💲 Financial Problem

WeHeal offers the following features to ensure that you are always in your comfort zone:

- ⌨ Anonymous Chat
- 💌Write ANONYMOUS LETTERS to share your feelings and concerns
- 📬 Receive replies to your letters from people across the WORLD
- ✒️ Write a QUOTE to inspire others
- 👓 Read quotes to get INSPIRED
- 💭 Read inspirational Short Stories
- 📝 Write replies to HELP others
- 👁️ Scroll through letters, quotes, stories & replies from people all around you


ANONYMOUS CHAT ⌨
Introducing anonymous chats so that whenever you need quick and instant help or whenever you want someone who can listen to you, help is at a click. You can use our anonymous chat feature to connect with people across the globe to have a conversation instantly. We understand that sometimes you just need to talk to someone and you can't wait 🙂


ANONYMOUS LETTERS 💌

We, at WeHeal, understand that everyone has a fear to be judged and a situation when we are moving through rough times, getting judged by people around can only get worse. But not to worry. Introducing anonymous letters! You can describe the situation that makes you feel low or rough times that you want to sail through in a letter which would be completely anonymous. Yes, you read that right! You do not even have to sign up to write a letter. People across the world will provide you with remedies to face your difficult times as soon as they read it and in no time you will be fine. Not to forget, you will be anonymous 🙂


REPLY 📝

As humans, we move through a lot of different situations in our lives no matter how old we are. Moving through these situations, we gain a lot of experience which we can use to help others who are moving through difficult times. Sharing experiences and giving advice is made all the more easy with WeHeal. You can view letters written by people near and far describing their problems which you can reply to at a click.

STORY 💭
Let your mind fly all around while you write real/fictional stories to inspire the world. You can write stories based on true events or you can even make up stories to make the readers feel good while you attract followers. After all, for a writer, even sky isn't the limit.

QUOTE ✒️

Can a morning be more beautiful than a one that starts with something inspirational to kick-off the day? We think it can't be. Not just mornings, it's always a wonderful feeling to read something inspirational that motivates you to your veins. With WeHeal, you can read short quotes written by people all across the globe and you can share your recipe of inspiration with the world. Let's inspire the world!

Because

When no-one else does, WE UNDERSTAND YOU.
